# Weather Analytics Pipeline — crontab do servidor Lightsail
#
# Para instalar: crontab -e  (como usuário ubuntu)
# Para verificar: crontab -l
#
# Horários em UTC (BRT = UTC-3):
#   09:00 UTC = 06:00 BRT  → coleta matinal
#   01:00 UTC = 22:00 BRT  → coleta noturna
#
# O pipeline coleta os últimos 2 dias do Open-Meteo, grava no BigQuery
# e executa dbt run + dbt test.

0 9  * * * cd /home/ubuntu/app_weather && docker compose -f docker-compose.pipeline.yml run --rm weather-pipeline >> /home/ubuntu/app_weather/logs/cron.log 2>&1
0 1  * * * cd /home/ubuntu/app_weather && docker compose -f docker-compose.pipeline.yml run --rm weather-pipeline >> /home/ubuntu/app_weather/logs/cron.log 2>&1
